{"tid":364513,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"行李延誤可以點做","createTime":"2017-08-18T12:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T17:29:54.000Z","uid":52735,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6761bca0e670931d2798306196ea9addbb380518","tid":364513,"uid":52735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟就一家人返鄉下探婆婆<br />\n可惜一落飛機<br />\n有個人就走嚟話你地啲行李延誤<br />\n要聽日先送到嚟<br />\n咁都算 同佢講完個地址<br />\n佢地話太遠 要後日先送到<br />\n我返去都唔使兩個鐘車程<br />\n你老母同我講話遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是我地不滿<br />\n佢就話你聽朝自己過嚟拎<br />\n車錢我地自己出<br />\n屌佢老母 我地當然唔制<br />\n跟住佢地就不了了之<br />\n唔撚理我地<br />\n利申：啲行李有好多生果<br />\n諗住送婆婆<br />\n因為婆婆入咗院<br />\n而且我有屋企人有哮喘<br />\n有哮喘藥係行李<br />\n有啲咩事真係唔知點算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁多位有冇咩計謀可以幫幫忙？"},{"pid":"af6fc2c3aed21ab59b835d50212899dc6cd3d5cf","tid":364513,"uid":52735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"134ff5e7a1c6ac5dc22df93e4ada30a8d85d2e66","tid":364513,"uid":52735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:32:36.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"cf8fc5a93ed25928ac8c8ccda37650068aec031a","tid":364513,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:32:37.000Z","msg":"買過堆藥同水果"},{"pid":"a83ed7f1895b1b54414909407ea0f7d12aa909e5","tid":364513,"uid":64155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"邊度?"},{"pid":"1b81eb2b4c29a79df1887ab79d40856af61aeca1","tid":364513,"uid":52735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買過堆藥同水果</blockquote><br />\n人在異國 連邊度有得買都唔知 更遑論買到同一牌子 點買啊大佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c68a607487f60d2f119a8d86b71fcaab90acca","tid":364513,"uid":30768,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買過堆藥同水果</blockquote><br />\n人在異國 連邊度有得買都唔知 更遑論買到同一牌子 點買啊大佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你想點，你有第二啲方法咩，你有錢可能得嘅，冇錢嘅話仲想點，諗住屌下就會加速送俾你？"},{"pid":"8809cf4b4160777f08ae9813126f2dd6545b86a0","tid":364513,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"錢/時間"},{"pid":"178812fb24c74039afb0eb9ecd151e8aebfecc5f","tid":364513,"uid":54502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"除左claim保險仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aeef525440369e05aa0def9c453a6cb7d6cc1ce","tid":364513,"uid":10608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:38:51.000Z","msg":"等"},{"pid":"9bea04a13c248ae5ade59d416e952a0bfd339608","tid":364513,"uid":60716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"係機場大叫囉 發爛囉 唔係可以點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed62efb3fb1549bfa4a412b05d222ede11dc4b41","tid":364513,"uid":134711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"明日自己去攞。葯，不能等"},{"pid":"78f239a1ed2210e23e47ef0b5f20b8fca1049323","tid":364513,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明日自己去攞。葯，不能等</blockquote><br />\n葯你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038f64e7ef3bde82689ae353b071fbee1cf156e4","tid":364513,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"Claim保險"},{"pid":"3cfedc9bdb0f9e1b328b4ec3ca02852c00f04c0e","tid":364513,"uid":126376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"打去總部屌9佢"},{"pid":"c61bc8d67b457471d0d1a47149cd6871b5ed798b","tid":364513,"uid":13199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"哮喘藥冇跟身咩？全部喺曬喼？如果係嘅話唯有聽朝去機場自己拎，最多咪打去保險